    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Thanks for stopping by to check out my car! It has been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. It's super clean and ready for its next adventure with you behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great home!",
