    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) featuring the 3.6L flat-six M96 powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus. This driver-focused example boasts a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a precise 6-speed manual transaxle for optimal gear-spacing. The chassis remains composed, utilizing its original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry to provide the tactile, communicative steering synonymous with the marque. While showing honest patina from spirited road use, the mechanicals are sound with consistent compression across all cylinders and a leak-free undercarriage. A turn-key, naturally aspirated performance machine for the discerning purist.",
