      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a superior balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a rigorous inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic standards meet our professional criteria. With a documented service history and a clean interior, it represents an outstanding opportunity for the discerning driver seeking reliability without the premium of a new showroom model. Experience the confidence of a vehicle prepared for the road ahead.",
