    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and still looks great parked in the driveway. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it\u2019s ready for a new home and plenty more adventures. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that won't let you down, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
